quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  18,35,"Aca yinjira mumurima wiwe nawe yidoga muguhemukira umutima wiwe avuga ati:- sinibaza nagatoyi yuko uwu murima wanje wokwononekara"
  18,36,"Kandi sinibaza yuko hazoba umusi w’umuhero w’Isi, ninasubizwa ku Muremyi wanje ntankeka nzohasanga icicaro ciza gusumba iki"
  18,37,"Mugenzi wiwe amubwira nawe amwishura ati:- mbega uramuhakanye uwakuremye agukuye mw’ivu, no kw’ima ry’intanga, hanyuma nukugira umuntu akwiye"
  18,38,"Mugabo Imana niyo Muremyi wanje, kandi Umuremyi wanje sindamu gereranya n’ikindi kintu"
  18,39,"N’igihe winjiye mumurima wawe wavuze uti:- ibi vyose mfise nivyo Imana yanshakiye kumpa, n’ubushobozi ntiburonswa atari ubuhawe n’Imana, niwambona mfise aya matungo makeyi hamwe n’ibibondo bikeyi gusumba wewe"
  18,40,Kumbure Umuremyi wanje azompa ibindi vyiza gusumba uwo murima wawe n’ukuyiteramwo imituragaro y’inkuba ivuye mw’ijuru ugasanga iyo Si ibaye ubugararwa gusa bunyerera
  18,41,Canke amazi yayo akaba ari ayibira kugeza naho udashobora kuyaronka
  18,42,"Ivyamwa vyayo biba birakikujwe, aca atangura kugaragura ibiganza vyiwe kubijanye n’akigoro yagize, ibiti navyo biba vyahenutse biri hejuru y’ibitsina vyavyo, n’uguca avuga ati:- iyo ntagereranya Umuremyi wanje n’ikindi kintu"
  18,43,"Kandi ntiyari afise abantu bamufasha inyuma y’Imana yonyene, canke kuri wenyene ngo yifashishe"
  18,44,"Iyo mw’Ijuru ubwami nubw’Imana gusa yonyene w’ubuzima bwose, kandi niyo nziza kumpembo, kandi niyo nziza yukuzana ingaruka nziza"
  18,45,"N’ubagirire akarorero k’ubuzima bwo ngaha kw’Isi, bumeze nk’amazi tumanura avuye mubicu, hanyuma akivanga n’ibiterwa vy’aha kw’Isi hanyuma ivyo biterwa bigahinduka ivyatsi vyumye vyavungaguritse mugihe umuyaga uca ubigurura hirya no hino, n’Imana irafise ubushobozi buri hejuru y’ibintu vyose"